\begin_layout Problem
A spin 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

 system is known to be in an eigenstate of 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{S}\cdot\hat{\mathbf{n}}$
\end_inset

 with eigenvalue 
\begin_inset Formula $\hbar/2$
\end_inset

, where 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\mathbf{n}}$
\end_inset

 is a unit vector lying in the 
\begin_inset Formula $xz$
\end_inset

-plane that makes an angle 
\begin_inset Formula $γ$
\end_inset

